data.text:
Boom De Yah Da

Will and Alicia handle an important case that could net the firm a great deal of money, but their efforts hang in the balance when their old rival Louis Canning attempts to delay a deposition that is crucial to their argument. Meanwhile, Will and Diane are forced to stand up to Clarke Hayden, and an old enemy makes life complicated for Eli.

Alma Matters

Holmes' reconciliation with his father is tested once again when he and Watson discover he is keeping a secret that could affect them all.

My Aim Is True

Danny and Baez investigate a string of drive-by shootings, which they believe are tied to the recent release of six wrongly convicted prisoners.
